cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with the application of deep neural networks for whole brain segmentation on MRI scans. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of deep neural networks also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) categories. Additionally, the paper involves medical imaging (cs.MM) as it deals with MRI scans for neuroanatomy investigation.
